review_blob:
Pours burnt chocolate brown, aroma of pumpkin/molasses/cinnamon. Palate is left clean with minimal aftertaste. 

This is a fantastic fall beer. Once the weather starts to drop and football is being played...this is the perfect beer.
beer_name: Redhook Out of Your Gourd Pumpkin Porter

review_blob:
Crisp and sweet. The alcohol content of 6.7 presents itself nicely and blends with the apple. Not too sweet... reading the ingredients theres no corn syrup (phew, thats a relief).

I really like this cider and for the price you cannot beat it. Great cider from a great apple growing region...makes sense.
beer_name: Square Mile The Original Hard Apple Cider
